OL,5,G0900 Bargain-Loving Brits in the Sun
OL,6,     FWe meet climbing hostel owners Sam
OL,7,     Fand Rich. They have a coach-load
OL,8,     Fof guests about to arrive, giving
OL,9,     Fthem a "mountain to climb" to get
OL,10,     Feverything ready in time.
OL,11,G1000 Nightmare Tenants, Slum Landlords
OL,12,     FSusan and Gary's
OL,13,     Ftoo-good-to-be-true letting agent
OL,14,     Fbroke into their house and changed
OL,15,     Fthe locks. Paul learned that his
OL,16,     Ffather's tenant owed 20k in rent.
