OL,5,G1100 Traffic Cops
OL,6,     FDrink drivers are increasingly
OL,7,     Ftrying to come up with ways to
OL,8,     Fbeat the system. One driver claims
OL,9,     Fto have had a single swig of beer,
OL,10,     Fforcing the cops to wait 20
OL,11,     Fminutes.
