OL,5,G1830 Home and Away
OL,6,     FThe Matheson sisters have a double
OL,7,     Fdate. Sonny goes extra hard. John
OL,8,     Fhas a staffing crisis.
OL,9,G1900 GPs: Behind Closed Doors
OL,10,     FPatients attending the mobile
OL,11,     Fsurgery include a man suffering
OL,12,     Fmultiple nosebleeds, a case of
OL,13,     Flong covid, and someone opening up
OL,14,     Fabout their low mood and
OL,15,     Floneliness.
OL,16,G2000 Casualty 24/7: Every Second Counts
OL,17,     FIt's a busy night at Barnsley
OL,18,     FHopsital's casualty department, so
OL,19,     Fwhen Sister Benita arrives to head
OL,20,     Fthe shift, the corridors are
OL,21,     Falready packed full of patients.
